<h1><span id="Open_Sicilian_with_2...Nc6">Open Sicilian with 2...Nc6</span></h1>
<p>Here Black has decided to play Nc6 instead of d6 or other moves.  If Black plays pawn to d5 later on then he has saved a tempo by not playing d6 first.
</p>
<p><b>1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 Nc6</b>
</p>
